      • createDashboard

        public Optional<Dashboard> createDashboard(String id,
                                           Principal owner,
                                           boolean enabled)
        Creates a new dashboard instance, persists it in the storage and makes it available for other users.
        Parameters:
        id - the ID of the dashboard to be created
        owner - the owner of the dashboard to be created
        enabled - true if the dashboard should be enabled by default
        Returns:
        the newly created dashboard object or null if a dashboard with the given ID already exists.
